title: Plastic Sandwich Bags – Zip Food Bags – Transparent Lunch Bags with Ziplock Closure – 200 pcs Small Snack Bag – 7 x 8-inch Freezer Bags – Non-BPA Plastic – Reusable Sandwich Bags for School and Work
features: LUNCH TO-GO: Prep and enjoy your homemade lunch with the Caterserve sandwich bags! Robust, practical, and easy to use, these zip bags are a must-have for busy people who still want to enjoy a delicious homemade lunch at work.

DURABLE DESIGN: Our lunch bags are made of plastic. This durable and resilient material will not tear or break easily so you can carry your sandwich and snacks safely and efficiently. The food bags are transparent so you can quickly spot what’s inside.

LEAKPROOF DESIGN: The Caterserve small sandwich bags have an air-tight ziplock closure that seals in the flavours for a better experience. The lunch bags retain freshness and prevent odours so you can enjoy garlic or fish for lunch without worrying about the smell.

MULTIPURPOSE: Although great for sandwiches and snacks, our transparent lunch bags can also be used to store leftovers, veggies, smoothie mixes, meat, and fish. They are freezer-safe and reusable for more practicality.

FOR YOU AND THE KIDS: These resealable food bags are great for the family’s lunch at school or work. Use these versatile zip freezer bags to pack your kid’s sandwich and a little snack that he can enjoy on a break. The sandwich bags are completely free of toxins and BPA for enhanced safety.
